| commits `c868c48`, `28d0889` processed | `git log` shows only `8f2a019`, `2cd0814`, `5d63a41` — neither hash exists |
| "changeset swung back to ADR-0001 rank-harness" | No `rank.ts`, no test script, no `tsx` devDep, zero `*.test.*` files |
| "ADR-0002 slug/num/str now untracked leftovers" | `src/lib` holds only `cn.ts`, `format.ts` — no slug/num/str, working tree **clean** |

The workspace has reset to the base snapshot (`8f2a019`); the Docs Steward's v0.2.7 sync describes state that isn't present here. Nothing to triage, implement, or release.

